page.title: 05ECOLOGY - PENALLT
page.content: {HEDGEROW STUDY}AT PENALLT 30 metre length {WOODY SPECIES - Hawthorn,Ash,Hazel,Rowan,Holly,Dog Rose CLIMBING PLANTS - Honeysuckle,Bramble,Goosegrass,Woody Nightshade,Ivy. {PLANTS}GROWING IN THE SHELTER OF THE HEDGE - Rosebay Willow Herb,Fool's Parsley, Wood Avens, Herb Robert,Cinquefoil, Jack by the Hedge, Ground Ivy, Smooth Hawks Beard, Bluebell, Vetch, Red Campion, Stitchwort, Clover (Red and White), Lamb's Tongue Plantain, Wild Strawberry, Pineapple Weed. {GRASSES}- Cock's Foot Grass, Broom,Couch Grass,Bent.
